CustomField.description: Name of the analytic snapshot that captured the original data. Examples may be something like "Daily Login Count", "Total Loan Count", etc... You will use this unique name to filter down the data when reporting.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Unique name for the data store that is a name of the analytic snapshot that captured the original data. Examples may be something like "Daily Login Count", "Total Loan Count", etc... You will use this unique name to filter down the data when reporting.
CustomField.label: Unique Name
